'''大凌河蜥屬'''（[[屬|屬]]名：{{lang|la|''Dalinghosaurus''}}{{noteTag|1=有時也被誤記為「Dalingh'''e'''saurus」}}，意為「[[大凌河|大凌河]]的蜥蜴」），又名'''大凌河龍'''，是一种已灭绝的中型原始[[蜥蜴|蜥蜴]]，為現存[[中國鱷蜥|中國鱷蜥]]的近親，具有頗長的尾部和後肢。大凌河蜥生存于[[早白堊世|早白堊世]]的[[東亞|東亞]]，在[[熱河生物群|熱河生物群]]中是很常見的動物，化石發現於[[中國|中國]][[遼寧|遼寧]]西部的[[北票|北票]][[四合屯|四合屯]]<ref name="Ji">Ji, S. A. "A new long-tailed lizard from the Upper Jurassic of Liaoning, China". (編) Department of Geology, Peking University. ''Collected Works of International Symposium on Geological Science''. Seismological Publishing House. 1998: pp.496-505.</ref>與[[凌源|凌源]][[大王杖子鄉|大王杖子]]<ref name = "Ji04">{{ cite journal | author = Ji, S.-A.; Ji, Q. | title = "Postcranial Anatomy of the Mesozoic Dalinghosaurus (Squamata): Evidence from a New Specimen of Western Liaoning" | journal = Acta Geologica Sinica (English Edition) | volume = 78 | issue = 4 | year = 2004 | pages = 897-906 | issn = 1000-9515 | url = }}</ref><ref>{{ cite journal | author = 姬书安, 季强 | title = "记辽宁西部中生代大凌河蜥（有鳞类）一新头后骨骼化石" | journal = 地质学报 | volume = 78 | issue = 4 | year = 2004 | pages = 506 | issn = 0001-5717 | url = }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = 王原; Evans, S. E. | title = "中国化石两栖类和有鳞类研究进展：过去15年回顾" | journal = 古脊椎动物学报 | volume = 44 | issue = 1 | year = 2006 | pages = 60-73 | issn = 1000-3118 | url = http://www.ivpp.cas.cn/cbw/gjzdwxb/xbwzxz/200810/W020090813368841296171.pdf | access-date = 2018-11-25 | archive-date = 2020-05-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200507085103/http://www.ivpp.cas.cn/cbw/gjzdwxb/xbwzxz/200810/W020090813368841296171.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，以及東部的[[康平縣|康平]][[何家信|何家信]]地區<ref name = "Evans05">{{cite journal | author = Evans, S. E. | title = "The Early Cretaceous lizard ''Dalinghosaurus'' from China" | journal = Acta Palaeontologica Polonica | volume = 50 | issue = 4 | year = 2005 | pages = 725–742 | issn = 0567-7920 | url = https://www.app.pan.pl/archive/published/app50/app50-725.pdf | access-date = 2018-11-25 | archive-date = 2017-02-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170223105938/http://www.app.pan.pl/archive/published/app50/app50-725.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 特徵描述與古生態學  ==
大凌河蜥全長 15 至 30 公分，其中尾部長度就佔了將近三分之二，另外其後肢長度也可達約 7 公分，兩者的長度相較之下都比大凌河蜥的近親長，趾爪相對較纖細，趾節也較粗壯；此外大凌河蜥的第四[[蹠骨|蹠骨]]比第三蹠骨長，而次末端[[趾骨|趾節]]（penultimate phalanx）則不比其他趾節長。中國[[古生物學家|古生物學家]][[姬書安|姬書安]]和[[季強|季強]]認為，這些特徵通常都存在於地棲性的蜥蜴身上，顯示大凌河蜥可能在開放的地面環境活動，且可能善於在地表奔跑<ref name = "Ji04"/>。古生物學家 Susan E. Evans 與[[王原_(古生物學家)|王原]]則認為，細長的末端趾節（ungual phalanx）顯示大凌河蜥可能同時也保有樹棲的習性，且待在樹上的時間應該會比在地面上的時間久<ref name = "Evans05"/>。

大凌河蜥的化石在[[熱河群|熱河群]]地層中很常見，光是收藏於[[古脊椎動物與古人類研究所|古脊椎動物與古人類研究所]]（IVPP）內的化石標本迄今就有11件，其中編號 IVPP V14234 的標本更保留了至少十個未成年的大凌河蜥個體。

另外，1990年代後期在[[北票|北票]]出土一具[[中華龍鳥|中華龍鳥]]化石（編號 NIGP 127587）的[[胃部|胃部]]也曾發現蜥蜴的殘骸<ref>{{ cite journal | author = Chen, P.; Dong, Z.; Zhen, S. | title = "An exceptionally well-preserved theropod dinosaur from the Yixian Formation of China" | journal = [[自然_(期刊)|Nature]] | volume = 391 | issue = 6663 | year = 1998 | pages = 147–152 | issn = 0028-0836 | doi = 10.1038/34356 | url = }}</ref>。2017年，[[英國|英國]][[布里斯托大學|布里斯托大學]]古生物學家 Fiann Smithwick 等人於針對這具殘骸加以分析比對，發現骨骸的特徵和大凌河蜥最為接近，加上大凌河蜥與中華龍鳥兩者的化石出土地點大致重合，顯示在當時大凌河蜥很可能是中華龍鳥的主食之一<ref>{{cite journal | author = Smithwick, F.M.; Nicholls, R.; Cuthill, I.C.; Vinther, J. | title = "Countershading and Stripes in the Theropod Dinosaur Sinosauropteryx Reveal Heterogeneous Habitats in the Early Cretaceous Jehol Biota" | journal = [[Current_Biology|Current Biology]] | volume = 27 | issue = 21 | year = 2017 | pages = pp.1–7, S1–2 | issn = 0960-9822 | doi = 10.1016/j.cub.2017.09.032 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/320624203_Countershading_and_Stripes_in_the_Theropod_Dinosaur_Sinosauropteryx_Reveal_Heterogeneous_Habitats_in_the_Early_Cretaceous_Jehol_Biota | access-date = 2018-11-25 | archive-date = 2020-11-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201105194947/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/320624203_Countershading_and_Stripes_in_the_Theropod_Dinosaur_Sinosauropteryx_Reveal_Heterogeneous_Habitats_in_the_Early_Cretaceous_Jehol_Biota | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
 
